{
  "stem": "13911.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but first, when we were in that place where I was bombed, where we had bombed, the whole group of people ate because he exchanged them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we bought food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the whole group was feeding because there wasn't such a thing as mine and-- we-- it's-- it's--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was sharing among--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wish-- I wish it would be like this, in this world of ours, that you go a little bit beyond just I and me and me and I.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there wasn't such a thing like, oh, it's mine, and I-- I'll eat and you will starve.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We ate.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We all-- it was equally served.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, people started coming out and on the black market, even selling a secondhand dress or a pair of shoes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because how long can this one dress last?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the one shoe-- one pair of shoes?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- where am I?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I talk too much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you-- you've found this committee that was going to help?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- and they-- OK, and then you say OK, now we have somebody to take care of us, to tell us what's happening in the world and what is going to be with us.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they told us about in Berlin, there is an aliyah going from Greece, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Ships, going from Berlin, we go to Greece.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from there, go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because this was our next destination.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to go home, somewhere that you can call your home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Palestine was, of course, in dream of-- in dreams of Jews for ages, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], you know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jerusalem was-- was your place where you have to end, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- Were you-- were you looking forward to going there?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
